<text top="721" left="122" width="146" height="14" font="1">The situation in Croatia</text>
<text top="757" left="153" width="675" height="14" font="1">Letter dated 29 April 1997 from the Secretary-General addressed to the President of the Security Council</text>
<text top="775" left="153" width="79" height="14" font="1">(S/1997/343)</text>
